                <h1>&#039;That opportunity will always be there&#039;: Coach K welcomes grandson Michael Savarino to Duke men’s basketball</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/e22f123e-9513-4b65-98af-b8ad9441a3ff.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Michael&#x20;Savarino&#x20;will&#x20;join&#x20;Duke&#x20;as&#x20;a&#x20;walk-on,&#x20;playing&#x20;under&#x20;his&#x20;grandfather,&#x20;legendary&#x20;head&#x20;coach&#x20;Mike&#x20;Krzyzewski.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Michael Savarino will join Duke as a walk-on, playing under his grandfather, legendary head coach Mike Krzyzewski.</p>

